    "highCondition": "Erase fault memory. OR Check short circuit of all components where this type of fault is detected against each other. OR Disconnect central ECU and faulty PCVs and faulty auxiliary valve. OR Check short circuit of wire of AUX_V (X2/17) and wires of all other components where shorted channels were detected against each other. Repair wire if faulty. OR If wire is OK, then reconnect the valves and repeat the previous measurement. Replace the valves if short circuit was measured.",
